Subject: Server Decommission
Description: Hello...we would like to power off our old on-premise server this Friday. Our plan is to leave it powered off for 30 days, and then decommission the server. I wanted to know if we needed to do a proper shutdown of it, or if we can just do a hard shutdown.
Solution_Comment__c:
- there are  about 10+ computers that cannot be located that still communicate with the EPP server
- we setup User Remediation for USB devices with a custom notification
- in about 7 days the EPP server will be shut down from your end
Account_Name__c: University of Texas Health Science Center in Houston
